---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About
permalink: /about/
---

<section class="about">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
  </header>
  
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-text">
      <h2>About {{ site.title }}</h2>
      <p>This is where you can share information about yourself or your blog. Replace this with your own content.</p>
      
      <p>You might want to include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Who you are and what you do</li>
        <li>Why you started this blog</li>
        <li>Your expertise and background</li>
        <li>What readers can expect to find here</li>
        <li>How to contact you</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p>The best way to reach me is via email at <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">your-email@example.com</a>.</p>
      
      <div class="about-social">
        <h3>Connect with me</h3>
        <div class="social-links">
          {% if site.socials.twitter %}
            <a href="{{ site.socials.twitter }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
          {% endif %}
          
          {% if site.socials.github %}
            <a href="{{ site.socials.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">GitHub</a>
          {% endif %}
          
          {% if site.socials.linkedin %}
            <a href="{{ site.socials.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>